name: Josa Kenn
content:
Josa Kenn was a male Duros who lived during the waning years of the Galactic Republic.
Kenn worked for Hedrett Shipping and Investments as a crewmember of the Fricasseed Nerf, a YT-1300 light freighter. During the Clone Wars, he was aboard the ship when it collided with a comet fragement in the Cularin system and was left drifting in space. However, he and the rest of the crew of the Nerf were rescued by the Heroes of Cularin.
